value: This is the end of playable demo story.
We hope you enjoyed it as much as we enjoyed working on it.
We want to especially thanks all the patrons who made this project possible.
In case you wish to support or check out our previous game, make sure to visit it at [url]https://www.patreon.com/maverik[/url]
Also, you can leave the feedback at striveforpower@gmail.com.
All links can be found at the main menu.
Reception of this demo will help us make necessary adjustments to deliver a better creation.
